snippet.title: Serial Cleaners - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Hide behind cars, use stealth across a blood-soaked landscape and get to cleaning in this gameplay trailer for Serial Cleaners, as showcased during Day 2 of Guerrilla Collective 2021. Serial Cleaners is headed to PC and consoles in 2021.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
